OL,3,C'Cramped' Bibby Stockholm rooms could
OL,4,Cviolate human rights, MPs warn
OL,6,FMPs have warned that the "cramped"
OL,7,Frooms and "claustrophobic" conditions
OL,8,Fon board the barge for asylum seekers
OL,9,Fin Dorset could violate human rights.
OL,11,FA committee of MPs visited the
OL,12,FPortland vessel earlier this month
OL,13,Fand, in a letter to the Home Office,
OL,14,Fwarned the living conditions they saw
OL,15,Fwere causing poor mental health.
OL,17,FHome Affairs Committee chair, Diana
OL,18,FJohnson, said as many as six asylum
OL,19,Fseekers were having to share "small,
OL,20,Fcramped cabins" originally designed
OL,21,Ffor one person.
