OL,3,C'Cramped' Bibby Stockholm rooms could
OL,4,Cviolate human rights, MPs warn
OL,6,F"These crowded conditions were clearly
OL,7,Fcontributing to a decline in mental
OL,8,Fhealth for some of the residents, and
OL,9,Fthey could amount to violations of the
OL,10,Fhuman rights of asylum seekers," Ms
OL,11,FJohnson warned the Home Office.
OL,13,FThe Committee's main findings
OL,15,FThe Bibby Stockholm barge has been
OL,16,Fmoored in Portland since , and the
OL,17,Ffirst asylum seekers moved onto the
OL,18,Fvessel in August.
