OL,3,C'Cramped' Bibby Stockholm rooms could
OL,4,Cviolate human rights, MPs warn
OL,6,FIt has been a controversial strand of
OL,7,Fthe government's plan to tackle
OL,8,Fillegal migration and bring down the
OL,9,Festimated #8m daily cost of housing
OL,10,Fasylum seekers in hotels.
OL,12,FThe MPs also said they were
OL,13,F"concerned" about the impact the barge
OL,14,Fhas had on the local community, due to
OL,15,Fa "lack of consultation".
