OL,3,C'Cramped' Bibby Stockholm rooms could
OL,4,Cviolate human rights, MPs warn
OL,6,F"Whilst we understand Dorset Council
OL,7,Fis receiving #3,500 per occupied
OL,8,Fbedspace,Jconsultation and engagement
OL,9,Fwith the local community before a
OL,10,Fdecision to base theJvessel in
OL,11,FPortland, should have taken place," Ms
OL,12,FJohnson added.
OL,14,F"The Government must not forget that
OL,15,Fthose seeking asylum could have
OL,16,Fexperienced severe trauma. They are
OL,17,Fvulnerable young men who will be in
OL,18,Fneed of critical help.
